ADDENDUM A: THE REVISED UNITED STATESIAN SATIRE AMENDMENT

1. If this code is ever deployed to any official United Statesian municipal or
   federal servers, the deployer is strictly required to publish a screenshot 
   of the deployed flag to Reddit (ideally r/vexillology) to document the event.
   
